        "Node graph: ``` input(GainNode) ──── dryGain ─────────────────────────── output(GainNode) input ──── waveShaper ── toneFilter ── wetGain ── output ``` Gains: `dryGain.gain = 1 - wet`; `wetGain.gain = wet`."
      ],
